Viva Riva!;;51;;87;;R;;With the Democratic Republic of Congo suffering from a gasoline shortage, criminal Riva (Patsha Bay) comes back home with gasoline stolen from his sometime employer, Cesar (Hoji Fortuna). Determined to use his new wealth to have a good time, Riva hits the town with longtime friend J.M. (Alex Herabo). At a club, Riva meets gorgeous Nora (Manie Malone) and steals her away from her gangster boyfriend, Azor (Diplome Amekindra). With both Cesar and Azor after him, Riva struggles to stay alive.;;Drama;;Djo Munga;;2010;;Patsha Bay,Manie Malone,Hoji Fortuna,Marlene Longange,Diplome Amekindra,Alex Herabo,Angelique Mbumb,Nzita Tumba,Davly Ilunga,Romain Ndomba,Tomas Bie;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/viva_riva